title: Physio Network Research Review
description:
Looking for a better way to keep up to date?   

Meet the Physio Network app - your very own journal, right in your pocket!

Receive monthly research reviews from world-leading experts, and:
- Save time and money keeping up to date
- Receive reliable information in easy-to-understand summaries
- Become more confident and effective in your clinical practice 

What you get in your subscription:
- 12 reviews every month on the most recent and clinically relevant studies in physio, written by industry experts
- Audio recordings of each review
- Immediate access to our entire library of 1000+ reviews
- CPD/CEU points
- Access to our members-only Facebook group

Special learning features:
- Customize reviews by your favorite topics
- Audio versions of each review for learning on the go  
- Download reviews for offline learning 
- Favorite reviews to check out later
- Search our library of 1000+ reviews
- Quizzes and certificates of completion for CPD/CEU points 


Want to try it out? Getting started is simple: Download the Physio Network app now and start your 7-day free trial. 


Here’s what some of our customers had to say:

“Amazing! It is a very useful and highly recommended PD tool!”

“Nicely designed. Easy to navigate and fast to load.”

“Very simple to use layout makes finding and reading research articles easy.”

“Easy access to the latest research that fits with busy lives.”

“Great for on the go learning.”

“What the physio world needs.”


Have any questions or suggestions? If so, we’d love to hear from you. Our customer support team is just an email away - simply write to info@physio-network.com
